---
By: Satchidananda
Locus:
  Page: 158
  Verse: 10
Tags:
  - Fate
---
There is a Divine Plan behind everything, and if we allow ourselves to be
used by that unseen Force. ...many things can happen in a mysterious,
miraculous way. If we interfere with that Plan by introducing our own plan,
the egocentric plan, tension will be created.
